<p>
The editors of <i>The Heron&#8217;s Nest</i> extend our hearty congratulations to all of the above listed poets. And we offer our thanks to the readers who have made these selections. A more complete report and 
readers&#8217; comments on some of these poems and others will be included in the print edition of Volume XIII.<br> <br> 
<span style="font-weight: bold;">John Stevenson<br>Managing Editor</span>
</p>
